Package: rfc7030-est-client
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3 (>= 3.0.0), libcrypto3 (>= 3.0.0)
Maintainer: Lorenzo <lorenzo@example.com>
Description: RFC7030 EST Client
 A library and client implementation of EST Enrollment Protocol RFC 7030.
 This package provides a command-line client for enrolling certificates
 using the EST (Enrollment over Secure Transport) protocol.
 .
 Features:
  - Support for /cacerts, /simpleenroll, /simplereenroll endpoints
  - TLS authentication with client certificates
  - Basic authentication support
  - Pluggable TLS/X.509 backend architecture
  - Cross-platform compatibility
 .
 The client can be used to request certificates from EST servers
 and supports both TLS client authentication and basic authentication.
